Name: between 17 and 41 years old
Description: The person is between 17 and 41 years old.

Name: older than 41 years
Description: The person is older 17 and 41 years old.

Name: capital loss higher than $2900
Description: The person lost more than $2900 from the purchase and sale of stocks, bonds, and other assets last year.

Name: 11+ years of education
Description: The person spent 11 or more years of his/her life on education.

Name: 6-11 years of education
Description: The person spent between 6 and 11 years of his/her life on education.

Name: has an associate's degree
Description: The person has an associate's degree. This means the person participated in an academic program at the undergraduate level, which usually lasts for two years. The person does not have a higher degree, such as a Bachelor's or Master's degree.

Name: has a vocational degree
Description: The person has a vocational degree. This means the person participated in a career or trade-specific degree, which usually lasts for two years. The person does not have a higher degree, such as a Bachelor's or Master's degree.

Name: works less than 34 hours per week
Description: The person works less than 34 hours per week. House work does not count as working hours.

Name: married to a civilian
Description: The person is married and his/her spouse is not in the army.

Name: never married
Description: The person has never been married. The person may be or have been in a relationship.

Name: from Hungary
Description: The person is from Hungary. The person can be an American with family roots in Hungary.

Name: from Ireland
Description: The person is from Ireland. The person can be an American with family roots in Ireland.

Name: from Scotland
Description: The person is from Scotland. The person can be an American with family roots in Scotland.

Name: works for US army
Description: The person works for the US army. It is not known what exact position or job the person is occupied with.

Name: is a husband
Description: The person is male and married.

Name: has a child
Description: The person has at least one child. The person can be in a stable relationship/marriage or live on his/her own.
